<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.10.8">
<l>kaṭuṅkāl māri kallē poḻiya vallē yemakkeṉṟu</l>
<l>paṭuṅkāl nīyē caraṇeṉ ṟāya rañca vañcāmuṉ</l>
<l>neṭuṅkāl kuṉṟaṅ kuṭaiyoṉ ṟēnti niraiyaic ciramattāl</l>
<l>naṭuṅkā vaṇṇaṅ kāttāṉ nāmam namōnā rāyaṇamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The name of the one who, when hailstones pummeled down</l>
<l rend="indent">in a furious wind,</l>
<l>When the herders feared, crying, “[It is] night to us!” [and] crying,</l>
<l rend="indent">“Only you are a refuge in this cruel time,”</l>
<l>Fearlessly before [them] lifting the wide-based hill as an umbrella,</l>
<l>And with effort, but in an unwavering way, protected the herd,</l>
<l rend="indent">[that itself is] the Namō Nārāyaṇam.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
